<h2>Directions: Camden Market-Passage</h2>
<p>Hire a bike from Castlehaven Road near the Camden Market.</p>
<p>Walk the bike back towards Camden Market and cross over to the other side of the road. To get onto Regent's Canal, look for the path marked Camden Lock East Yard.</p>
<p>Once you're on the canal, continue under the bridge and cycle towards Islington. Remember, pedestrians have priority at all times.</p>
<p>When you can't go any further along the canal (because of the tunnel), take the path up to the left. On Muriel Street, continue left followed by a right onto Carnegie Street.</p>
<p>Continue left on Charlotte Terrace and then right onto Copenhagen Street.</p>
<p>Turn right using the cycle link onto Cloudesley Road and left on Ritchie Street.</p>
<p>The route continues straight ahead on Bromfield Street. Using the cycle link, continue to the left.</p>
<p>At the traffic lights, continue straight ahead over the junction and walk your bike along the Camden Passage.</p>
<h2>Camden Passage to Exmouth Market</h2>
<p>Continue to the right. After the Camden Passage, continue straight ahead to re-join Upper Street.</p>
<p>Keep going straight, over the junction, and then take a right turn onto Arlington Way. You'll pass by Bobbin Bicycles.</p>
<p>Turn right at the end of Arlington Way.</p>
<p>Turn left on Rosoman Street just after Finsbury Town Hall. Exmouth Market is located on the right.</p>
</div>
