<h2>Exmouth Market to Spitalfields Market</h2>
<p>Continue straight down Skinner Street, along the cycle path, and turn right onto St. John Street.</p>
<p>Continue straight ahead, over Clerkenwell Road, and you'll reach Smithfield Market. Take a left onto Charterhouse Street and then the next right onto Lindsey Street.</p>
<p>Head left onto Long Lane and continue straight ahead over the junction.</p>
<p>Keep going straight ahead. Beech Street will become Chiswell Street.</p>
<p>When you reach Finsbury Square, turn left and then take the next right. Continue straight ahead onto Christopher Street.</p>
<p>Take the next right followed by the second left onto Sun Street and follow the road as it curves to the left and becomes Appold Street.</p>
<p>Turn right on to Primrose Street and, at the end, there will be a docking station on the left. Spitalfields Market is straight ahead.</p>
